videos.description: Duke's Harry Giles showed off his athleticism with this play in the first half against Wake Forest.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCB One Play (Giles with the impressive putback slam) 2017/01/28 ESHEET

videos.headline: Giles with the impressive putback slam

videos.description: Brandon Childress hits the floater to help Wake Forest maintain its narrow lead in the first half.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCB One Play (Childress keeps Wake Forest ahead early) 2017/01/28 ESHEET

videos.headline: Childress keeps Wake Forest ahead early

videos.description: Keyshawn Woods nails the 3-pointer to help increase Wake Forest's first-half lead over Duke.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCB One Play (Woods hits from beyond arc to build Wake Forest lead) 2017/01/28 ESHEET

videos.headline: Woods hits from beyond arc to build Wake Forest's lead

videos.description: Grayson Allen throws the pass away, which allows Wake's Bryant Crawford to finish on the other end, plus the foul.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCB One Play (Allen turnover leads to Wake hoop) 2017/01/28 ESHEET

videos.headline: Allen turnover leads to Wake hoop

videos.description: Luke Kennard is trying to bring Duke back after converting the jumper and drawing the foul.
videos.headline: Kennard hits and-one jumper

videos.description: Duke's Grayson Allen and Wake's Bryant Crawford jaw at each other after a blocking foul on Allen, resulting in the Duke star getting a technical.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCB One Play (Allen called for technical foul) 2017/01/28 ESHEET

videos.headline: Allen called for technical foul

videos.description: Brandon Childress finds John Collins down low for the flush, as Wake Forest looks to pull out a win against Duke.
videos.headline: Collins slams one home for Wake

videos.description: After a Grayson Allen foul, things got heated and Wake Forest was assessed a technical foul.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCB One Play (Duke and Wake involved in heated exchange) 2017/01/28 ESHEET

videos.headline: Heated exchange late in Duke's win vs. Wake

videos.description: Keyshawn Woods banks in a jumper with the shot clock winding down, as Wake tries to hold on against Duke late.
videos.headline: Bank is open for Wake Forest's Woods

videos.description: Duke's Grayson Allen continues his eventful game by hitting a 3-pointer to cut the Wake Forest lead to one point.
videos.headline: Allen hits from beyond the arc to put pressure on Wake

videos.description: Luke Kennard gives Duke a late two-point lead after hitting from beyond the arc with under seven seconds left.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCB One Play (Kennard hits late go-ahead 3-pointer for Duke) 2017/01/28 ESHEET

videos.headline: Kennard hits late game-winner for Duke

videos.description: Luke Kennard's late 3-ball proves to be the difference in Duke's 85-83 win over Wake Forest.
videos.headline: Kennard gives Duke late victory

videos.description: C.L. Brown shares how Duke felt about its hectic week and what a comeback win over Wake Forest means for the Blue Devils moving forward.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCB Analysis (Duke hoping win can right the ship) 2017/01/28 ESHEET SC

videos.headline: Duke hoping win can right the ship
